  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AESDecryptData

    AESEncryptData
    This function uses AES to encrypt string columns that are passed to it.
    AESEncryption
    A class that performs AES encryption / decryption on strings.
    FPEDecryptData
    This function decrypts FPE encrypted string columns that are passed to it.

    A simple function that sets the value of any column it receives to "Hello World" and returns the result.
